title: Lose the Gut (Good Omens Dub)
author: Len Dubs
comment: This is why my confidence and self esteem has shot up ever since I started getting into Good Omens. This stuff right here.
Hell yeah fluffy people are the best! Hugging one is like hugging a marshmallow and it's amazing!

And that's another thing we can thank good Omens for. first getting me out of a Narnia sized closed. (with special thanks to the freeborn and Whiteley) and portraying fluffy people as someone to wrap you're self in and love to bits
